    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and delivers solid performance, while the transmission shifts smoothly for a comfortable ride. The interior is clean with only minor wear consistent with its age, and the exterior paint retains a nice shine despite a few small, typical blemishes. It\u2019s a dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
      "price": 33500.0,
